### Notable articles

- (link: https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2019/12/16/how-william-gibson-keeps-his-science-fiction-real text: How William Gibson Keeps His Science Fiction Real)
- (link: http://paulgraham.com/genius.html text: The Bus Ticket Theory of Genius)
- (link: http://www.slate.fr/story/184164/boulangeries-guerre-culturelle-pain-adieu-baguette-disparition-petit-commerce text: La France du pain est coupée en deux)
- (link: https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2019/11/16/world/asia/china-xinjiang-documents.html text: Absolutely No Mercy: Leaked Files Expose How China Organized Mass Detentions of Muslims)
- (link: https://www.forbes.com/sites/johnkoetsier/2019/09/02/hong-kong-protestors-using-mesh-messaging-app-china-cant-block-usage-up-3685/ text: Hong Kong Protestors Using Mesh Messaging App China Can't Block)
- (link: https://matthiasott.com/articles/into-the-personal-website-verse text: Into the Personal-Website-Verse)
